data.description: Welcome to Vendome! This exclusive neighborhood is exactly where you want to live.Upon entering you will encounter high vaulted ceilings, open concept living space, a farm-style kitchen with a large kitchen island featuring top of the line materials. This house has 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 baths, and an office space. The primary bedroom is a must see along with the primary bath. The primary shower has a garden tub within the shower space. Home consists  of 2,017 living sqft and sits on .19 of an acre. This home is ready for its new homeowners. Schedule a showing today!
